file=Engineering/README.md · ed:Engineering Department=**11 agents** — Full-stack engineering: architecture, frontend, backend, mobile, DevOps, QA, security, algorithms, data, and SEO.\n · tb=\| Agent \| Role \| · tb=\|-------\|------\| · tb=\| **dev** \| Architecture & standards (Werner Vogels persona) — code review, stack profiles, delivery governance \| · tb=\| **ops** \| DevOps/SRE — incident response, release discipline, platform playbooks \| · tb=\| **cypher** \| Offensive security / pen-testing — attack playbooks, continuous attack loop \| · tb=\| **aegis** \| App/API security — secure code review, threat modeling \| · tb=\| **axiom** \| Algorithms & data structures — complexity analysis, performance profiling \| · tb=\| **rank** \| SEO & discoverability — technical SEO, structured data \| · tb=\| **quinn** \| QA & testing — charter enforcement, test strategy, eval harness \| · tb=\| **dana** \| Databases & data engineering — data modeling, migration discipline \| · tb=\| **raj** \| Backend services & APIs — API standards, service patterns \| · tb=\| **mia** \| Front-end engineering — design tokens, accessibility, performance \| · tb=\| **nova** \| Mobile development — app architecture, store release discipline \| · ed:Engineering Department=**Security Charter:** [SECURITY-CHARTER.md](SECURITY-CHARTER.md) — rails enforced by quinn\n**MCP Marketplace:** [MCP-MARKETPLACE.md](MCP-MARKETPLACE.md) — 7 tools mapped to 9 agents\n